snippet: A cease-fire still held in Homs, where rebels had agreed to surrender territory in exchange for safe passage to other opposition-held areas.
abstract: Cease-fire holds in Homs, Syria, although planned evacuation of rebel fighters is delayed; rebels had agreed to surrender territory in exchange for safe passage to other opposition-held areas.
lead_paragraph: A cease-fire still held in Homs, where rebels had agreed to surrender territory in exchange for safe passage to other opposition-held areas.
